data.description: OVER $15,000 PRICE IMPROVEMENT & NOW VACANT, MOVE-IN READY! SELLER CONCESSIONS AVAILABLE - MAKE AN OFFER! MOTIVATED SELLER!  Welcome to a charming and completely renovated home featuring a new roof, modern stainless-steel appliances, and gorgeous Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) flooring throughout. Situated in a quiet and established neighborhood, this home is located near Pensacola NAS and our breathtaking Gulf Coast beaches, with a short 15-minute drive to downtown Pensacola. Perfectly suited for first-time homebuyers, military personnel, or retirees, this residence showcases an open living area adorned with an inviting electric, herringbone hearth fireplace. The remodeled kitchen boasts new cabinets, countertops, and appliances, seamlessly flowing into an adjacent dining area. The primary bedroom is generously proportioned, complete with an en suite bathroom. Embrace the spacious lot with an ample backyard, providing a safe haven for little ones and pets to play freely. Schedule a showing today to see this wonderful property!
